Formation-Longmaxi Formation in Jiaoshiba Block as target
stratum, output in test up to 20.3  104 m3/d and breakthrough
made in exploration in the end. In 2013, Sinopec started
development of test well group and carried out evaluation of
production and construction in Jiaoshiba Block [44].
Yanchang Petroleum, Huadian Group and Shenhua Group
have carried out a large amount of exploration of marine,
